text: BK Häcken is an association football club on the island of Hisingen in the town of Gothenburg in Sweden. The men's soccer team won the Swedish Cup during the seasons of 2015–2016, 2018–2019, 2022-2023 and 2024–2025. It also won the 2022 edition of Allsvenskan and became Swedish champions for first time. ==References== == Other websites == *Official website Category:1940 establishments in Europe Category:Swedish football clubs Category:1940s establishments in Sweden
